{"tid":2249503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊朗武器禁令解封 中俄倡合作","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T06:42:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c59e213cdd15910bb857511d1f867009d240d73a","tid":2249503,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/2475OUHCCVHSJAHHFP267KT42Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2F2475OUHCCVHSJAHHFP267KT42Y%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=cf03b950\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201019%2F2475OUHCCVHSJAHHFP267KT42Y%2F&h=5b95a70f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201019/2475OUHCCVHSJAHHFP267KT42Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n伊朗武器禁令解封 中俄倡合作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/avVXw4NEHCXzyfsuTdpSlBkoxG8=/1624x1083/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SYDC5ZWF5BADTPYROBGS7RYHP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FavVXw4NEHCXzyfsuTdpSlBkoxG8%3D%2F1624x1083%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSYDC5ZWF5BADTPYROBGS7RYHP4.jpg&h=6709d54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■武器禁運停止令伊朗可合法買賣常規武器。路透社<br />\n<br />\n聯合國針對伊朗實施的武器禁令昨日屆滿，伊朗形容是國際社會的歷史時刻，強調伊朗今後毋須大舉購買軍備。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗外交部昨日發表聲明，稱針對進出伊朗的武器轉移及相關活動，以及金融服務的所有限制，全部自動終止，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美促延長遭聯國否決<br />\n<br />\n伊朗外長扎里夫指，伊朗與國際社會軍事合作將會正常化，是地區多邊主義、和平與安全的勝利，又形容昨日是國際社會重要時刻，因各國為了保護安理會決議和核協議，抵抗美國惡意。而莫斯科早在上月提出準備好與德黑蘭加強軍事合作，北京亦稱願意在限期禁令屆滿後向德黑蘭售武。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗2015年7月與美國、英國、法國、俄羅斯、中國和德國達成伊朗核問題協議，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"dff6ad456e02b02b9c153e0c1bbdb296b201d88c","tid":2249503,"uid":88737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"以色列好快又日日放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387e0fbaab9aae72047d1250cdb3d36fb41d8977","tid":2249503,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff6ad456e02b02b9c153e0c1bbdb296b201d88c","tid":2249503,"uid":88737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"以色列好快又日日放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"隻揪既話以色列打到佢變煙花"},{"pid":"1d752fa09a6d1888b7d3c4eacc62d61bdb995c6c","tid":2249503,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387e0fbaab9aae72047d1250cdb3d36fb41d8977","tid":2249503,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff6ad456e02b02b9c153e0c1bbdb296b201d88c","tid":2249503,"uid":88737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"以色列好快又日日放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"隻揪既話以色列打到佢變煙花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就睇下以色列嘅架生勁定俄系架生勁"},{"pid":"ab7c5de18e3668ecfb3637a0499e1757905bf01f","tid":2249503,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d752fa09a6d1888b7d3c4eacc62d61bdb995c6c","tid":2249503,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387e0fbaab9aae72047d1250cdb3d36fb41d8977","tid":2249503,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff6ad456e02b02b9c153e0c1bbdb296b201d88c","tid":2249503,"uid":88737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"以色列好快又日日放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"隻揪既話以色列打到佢變煙花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/ca